dct_title_s: Topographic map of Yosemite National Park, California
dct_description_sm: Surveyed between 1893 and 1909, roads and trails added 1928 by National Park Service.; Relief shown by contour lines and spot heights.; Contour interval 100 feet.; "Hetch Hetchy and Lake Eleanor reservoirs shown in hatched blue lines; from approximate information only."
